    <item>
      <title>莫迪有望在选举中赢得压倒性胜利：这将对市场产生什么影响？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/modi-set-for-landslide-election-win-what-are-the-implications-for-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Anand Rathi Wealth 副首席执行官 Feroze Azeez 分析了印度选举结果对经济和金融资产的影响。出口民调显示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党在大选中大获全胜，印度股市、债券和卢比均大幅上涨。Azeez 在“彭博市场：亚洲”节目中发表讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/modi-set-for-landslide-election-win-what-are-the-implications-for-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 04:53:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
