      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/macau-tourism-head-city-on-target-to-hit-33-million-visitors-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 04:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
